      "span_text": "The effect of a somatosenso ry task on human brain metabolism and blood flow has been measured by several investigators (Halsey et aI., 1979;  Ginsberg et aI., 1987 Ginsberg et aI., , 1988 , who all found focal activation of the contralateral sensory-motor cortex.",
